<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Support</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("header", { headerTitle: "Support" }) %>

  <div class="page-banner">
    <div class="page-banner-inner">
      <h1>We're Here to Support You</h1>
      <p>You're not alone — help is always available</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="resource-grid">

      <div class="resource-card">
        <svg class="resource-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#BB1B36" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="5" r="3"/><path d="M12 8v6"/><path d="M8 22l4-8 4 8"/><path d="M6 12h12"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Take a Break</h3>
        <p>Step outside for a short walk or find a quiet space to breathe and reset.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resource-card">
        <svg class="resource-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#BB1B36" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Talk to Someone</h3>
        <p>Reach out to a friend, family member, or someone you trust about how you're feeling.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resource-card">
        <svg class="resource-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#BB1B36" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Mindfulness</h3>
        <p>Try a calming breathing or meditation exercise to stay present and grounded.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="resource-card">
        <svg class="resource-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#BB1B36" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Professional Help</h3>
        <p>If you feel persistently low, consider talking to a counsellor or mental health professional.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="emergency-banner mt-3">
      <h3>Need immediate help?</h3>
      <p>Call <strong>Lifeline: 13 11 14</strong> (24/7) or <strong>Beyond Blue: 1300 22 4636</strong></p>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--color-text-muted);">In an emergency, call 000</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-3 text-center">
      <a href="/mood" class="btn btn-primary">Log Your Mood</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("footer") %>
</body>
</html>
